===Noun===
'''spouse''' (''plural'' '''[[spouses]]''')

#A [[husband]] or [[wife]] ([[irrespective]] of [[sex]]).
#A [[wife]]'s [[husband]] is her [[spouse]]; a [[husband]]'s [[wife]] is his [[spouse]].

